## move tarball to opt folder
sudo tar -xvzf [WebStorm-2021.3.tar.gz] -C /opt

## Change permissions on a locked opt folder
sudo chmod 777 -R /opt/

## Setting up nginix locally
1. Install nginx
 - sudo apt update
 - sudo apt install nginx
 
2. Start|Stop|Restart|Reload|Disable nginx using
 - sudo systemctl [start|stop|restart|reload|disable] nginx
 
3. Postgres connection
 - sudo -u postgres psql

3. Setting up a project on linode
 - Database environment should be set
 - Create a directory on the linode server and pull your project into it
 - Do your docker configuration setup - ( If any )
 - Set up project on kong (Connection between the cl)
 	> Set up Services
 	> Set up Targets
 	
 
 	

